  </m:mrow>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-58">Comparing above two equations, we see that magnitude of total mechanical energy is equal to kinetic energy, but different in sign. Hence,
</para>
<para id="element-59">
<m:math display="block">
  <m:mrow>
    <m:mi>E</m:mi>
