</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-62">These relations are very significant. We shall find resemblance of forms of energies in the case of Bohr’s orbit as well. In that case, nucleus of hydrogen atom and electron form the two – body system and are held together by the electrostatic force. 
</para>
<para id="element-63">Importantly, it provides an unique method to determine other energies, if we know any of them. For example, if the system has mechanical energy of 
